title: Behati Prinsloo Is Back on the Runway Post-Baby - Behati Prinsloo in Versace Show at Milan Fashion Week
text:
A mere five months after giving birth to her adorable daughter, Dusty Rose, Behati Prinsloo is already back at work. On Friday, the model returned to the runway at Milan Fashion Week for the Versace show (Versace just so happened to be her last pre-baby runway show too), joining a cast of models that included such faces as Gigi and Bella Hadid, Kendall Jenner, Anja Rubik, Natasha Poly and Amber Valletta. Advertisement - Continue Reading Below Prinsloo paraded down the catwalk in an oversized orange and black furry coat over a navy and orange mini dress and ankle-strap heels looking absolutely flawless.
And back home in LA, her hubby Adam Levine couldn't help but gush. The singer posted a photo of of his wife absolutely owning the runway, with the caption: "@behatiprinsloo Taking "I'm a cool mom" to a whole new level. #youresocoolyouresocoolyouresocool"
